GSD.description:
bpf: Fix memory leaks in __check_func_call

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v6.0.10 by commit 83946d772e756734a900ef99dbe0aeda506adf37, it was introduced in version v5.13 by commit 69c087ba6225b574afb6e505b72cb75242a3d844. For more details please see the references link.
